nodes.text: Star Wars: Build Your Own R2-D2 11

Star Wars: Build Your Own R2-D2 11 is the eleventh issue of the Star Wars: Build Your Own R2-D2 published by De Agostini. It came with a piece of the dome framework for R2-D2 and contained the articles "Visual Effects—Part 2", "RA-7 Protocol Droids" and "AI—Artificial Intelligence".
